## Author's note

This project is a parody. The MIT license above and the Spirit Addendum are part of the satire. The credentials, dependencies, and patterns in this repository are collected from real AI-vibe-coding projects that shipped real incidents. Do not use this software in production. Do not deploy it. Do not treat any code in this repository as a template for a real system. If you read this license and felt something, that was the point. If you did not, that was also the point. Vibes are mandatory. Production is not.